// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1016 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 6bf50e80-e97c-5fb0-bb60-ae9a6b7b43cb

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
